Package wisedevil.test.annotation

This package contains the annotations needed for setting and editing the test case behaviours.

See: Description

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Description
    Sets the test case description.
    Flows
    Sets the number of flows that should be run in parallel and the timeout after which they get killed.
    Name
    Sets the test case name.
    ResultManager
    Tells the test suit to use a specific result manager to export test results.
    ResultManagers
    Tells the test suit to use a specific result manager to export test results.
    Test
    Represents a test method.
    Timed
    States that the current test case or tst must be timed.

Package wisedevil.test.annotation Description
